y servants have cattle:","year":-1452},{"id":"recDg9hDbCTNiiMi4","ref":"Num.32.5","text":"Wherefore, said they, if we have found grace in thy sight, let this land be given unto thy servants for a possession, and bring us not over Jordan.","year":-1452},{"id":"recV6Dmh34sy7p3mR","ref":"Num.32.6","text":"And Moses said unto the children of Gad and to the children of Reuben, Shall your brethren go to war, and shall ye sit here?","year":-1452},{"id":"recdLTrEz5bQhA2SH","ref":"Num.32.7","text":"And wherefore discourage ye the heart of the children of Israel from going over into the land which the LORD hath given them?","year":-1452},{"id":"recyMH0oTdTm0Pams","ref":"Num.32.8","text":"Thus did your fathers, when I sent them from Kadeshbarnea to see the land.","year":-1452}]}
